text: Building at 810 Wabash Avenue is a historic commercial building located at Terre Haute, Vigo County, Indiana. It was built about 1870, and is a two- story, rectangular, Italianate style brick building. It features an elaborate cast iron storefront on the first story and round arched windows on the second.
